I sell products using Gumroad. If I&#x27;m not a developer it&#x27;s not easy to build a custom storefront where I want to display all of my products.<p>So I built a woocommerce extension(wordpress plugin) which imports all of my products from gumroad and integrates gumroad checkout system.
Plugin: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;wordpress.org&#x2F;plugins&#x2F;gumpress&#x2F;
Demo storefront: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gumpress.io&#x2F;demo1&#x2F;<p>Right now it&#x27;s very basic, imports all gumroad products and display gumroad checkout popup on &quot;Buy now&quot; button click.<p>I&#x27;d love to get all of your feedback, questions, and comments.
